list out all wired and wireless protocols
Here is a list of some common wired and wireless communication protocols:

Wired Protocols:

Ethernet (IEEE 802.3)
RS-232
RS-485
USB (Universal Serial Bus)
CAN (Controller Area Network)
Modbus
Profibus
Fieldbus Foundation
HART (Highway Addressable Remote Transducer)
BACnet (Building Automation and Control Network)
Wireless Protocols:

Wi-Fi (IEEE 802.11)
Bluetooth
Zigbee
Z-Wave
NFC (Near Field Communication)
RFID (Radio Frequency Identification)
LoRaWAN (Long Range Wide Area Network)
Sigfox
Cellular (2G, 3G, 4G, 5G)
Satellite (GPS, GLONASS, Galileo)
Note that this list is not exhaustive and there are many other wired and wireless communication protocols available for different applications and industries.
